   To Contact Northern PlainFacts:
   For comments/questions e-mail us at:
   plainfacts-owner@listserver.sidney.ars.usda.gov .

   To Contact NPARL:
   USDA-ARS Northern Plains Agricultural Research Laboratory
   1500 North Central Avenue
   Sidney, Montana 59270

   Phone: 406-433-2020
   Fax: 406-433-5038
   Internet:
   http://www.sidney.ars.usda.gov

   NPARL Policy:
   The Northern Plains Agricultural Research Laboratory has an open door
   policy and its staff is available to help you find the answers to your
   agricultural questions. If we do not have the expertise within our
   immediate organization, we stand ready to connect you with a specialist
   who can address your needs.
